  "description": "A breathtaking panoramic view of a city nestled alongside a body of water, all bathed in the vibrant hues of a sunrise or sunset. The sky is a dramatic display of color, featuring fiery orange and deep pink clouds stretching across the horizon. These clouds are long and wispy, creating a sense of movement and grandeur. Below, the city lights twinkle, contrasting with the fading darkness. A layer of mist or fog hangs over the water, adding depth and mystery to the scene. The foreground shows a lush, green hillside with trees, providing a natural frame for the urban landscape. The overall composition evokes a sense of tranquility and awe.",
